    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1897-02-01T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1897-02-01T00:00:00-05:00" n="699"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d699">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Message of the President.</hi>
                </head>
                <p rend="flushleft">
                    <hi rend="italic">To the Senate:</hi>
                </p>
                <p>I transmit herewith, in response to a resolution of the Senate of the 6th ultimo,
                    a report from the Secretary of State, accompanied by copies of correspondence
                    concerning the arrest, imprisonment, trial, and condemnation to perpetual
                    imprisonment in chains of Julio Sanguily, a citizen of the United States, by the
                    authorities of Spain in Cuba.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Grover Cleveland.</hi>
                    </signed>
                    <lb/>
                    <dateline rendition="#left">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Executive Mansion</hi>,<lb/>
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1897-02-01">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 1, 1897</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
